Package org.universAAL.ri.api.manager

Common core classes of the manager.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    RemoteAPI
    Interface that defines the methods of the Remote API, that will be available through the server HTTP endpoint, according to the R-API documentation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Activator
    OSGi Activator to start everything.
    Configuration
    Helper class to centralized access to configuration parameters, which should help when porting to uAAL Config Manager.
    RemoteAPIImpl
    Implementation of the RemoteAPI interface.
    RemoteUAAL
    Extension of the Utility API UAAL helper class that adds a few small tweaks to acomodate remote node information.
